# GitHub Packages — both scopes resolve from npm.pkg.github.com (ADR-004).
# Auth comes from the NODE_AUTH_TOKEN env var (classic PAT with read:packages —
# must cover BOTH orgs: theamazingwolf for sport-*, StormForgeVentures for ciyp-*).
# Never put a literal token in this file. CI supplies NODE_AUTH_TOKEN per workflow.
@theamazingwolf:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
@stormforgeventures:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
